Author: jadyoyster
Content:
IIRC most of these anti-bacterial soaps contain this stuff: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Triclosan

It doesn't seem to lead to resistance either, but that doesn't make using those products any more sensible.

Author: trotsky
Content: Netflix actually wants low ranked service provider to agree to host edge caches for netflix's multi-service CDN, which saves them power and transit and lets them charge others to get on there.

Author: Helianthus
Content: I kinda do want to be mean.  This hurts my head, I already miss the side-by-side, where I could see the contiguous code.

Author: trotsky
Content: netflix content caps out at ~6mbps for HD, and for streams or equipment that doesn't support HD (not uncommon) that number is ~1.5mbps
